con:property.con:name: getData
con:property.con:value: SELECT BKNG_ID,ETS_APNTMT_ID,CUST_FST_NAM FROM BKNG WHERE BKNG_ID IN (SELECT DISTINCT BKNG.BKNG_ID FROM BKNG,TST,TST_VARTN WHERE BKNG.DLVY_MDE_CDE <> 'PBT' AND BKNG.BKNG_STS_TYP_CDE = 'RSRVD' AND TST.PGM_CDE = 'TEL' AND BKNG.TST_ID = TST.TST_ID AND TST_VARTN.TST_ID = BKNG.TST_ID MINUS SELECT HLD.BKNG_ID FROM HLD) AND DATE_CREATED IS NOT NULL AND CUST_FST_NAM LIKE 'shfirst%' ORDER BY DATE_CREATED DESC
